Source: rexxcurl
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Mark Hessling <mark@rexx.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 5), autotools-dev
Standards-Version: 3.8.3

Package: rexxcurl-tools-regina
Architecture: any
Section: devel
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Provides: rexxcurl-tools
Conflicts: rexxcurl-tools-rexxtrans, rexxcurl-tools-oorexx
Description: Rexx interface to libcurl; http://curl.haxx.se/libcurl/
 This package provides the rexxcurl executable with the external functions embedded.
 Useful for checking should errors occur with rexxcurl-lib.

Package: rexxcurl-dev-regina
Architecture: any
Section: libdevel
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Provides: rexxcurl-dev
Conflicts: rexxcurl-dev-rexxtrans, rexxcurl-dev-oorexx
Description: Rexx interface to libcurl; http://curl.haxx.se/libcurl/
 This package provides the external function package as a static library
 and config scripts to statically link with your Rexx interpreter.

Package: rexxcurl-lib-regina
Architecture: any
Section: libs
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Provides: rexxcurl-lib
Description: Rexx interface to libcurl; http://curl.haxx.se/libcurl/
 This package provides the Rexx/CURL external function package
 installed into the Rexx interpreter's addons directory.

Package: rexxcurl-doc
Architecture: all
Section: doc
Provides: rexxcurl-doc
Description: Rexx interface to libcurl; http://curl.haxx.se/libcurl/
 This package provides documentation for Rexx/CURL.
